t May 6, 2026 image-caption record for Epstein note\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T04:38:13Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_5aa56aab2530_submitted-evidence-05-defendant-5aa56aab2530\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-05-defendant-5aa56aab2530.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Defense evidence on provenance, custody, and authentication. It reports DOJ's explanation that it never had the note, that the note had not yet been authenticated, that the note came through an unrelated Tartaglione attorney-client dispute, that it was in a court vault since 2021, and that DOJ lawyers involved in sealed proceedings could not disclose anything due to privilege restrictions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T04:39:50Z\",\"sha256\":\"5aa56aab25302158d1be6b80426ed4d517ee436cea958297c34e648148db2bca\",\"size_bytes\":2780,\"source_description\":\"Associated Press article by Ed White, retrieved via AP News page during defendant arguments; relevant text extraction from public article page.\",\"source_url\":\"https://apnews.com/article/jeffrey-epstein-suicide-note-5297f49736e625a06d0db3c7b737b997\",\"storage_name\":\"5a/5aa56aab25302158d1be6b80426ed4d517ee436cea958297c34e648148db2bca\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"AP May 7, 2026 report: DOJ seeing Epstein note for first time and authentication limits\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T04:34:52Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_757899113d89_submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-757899113d89\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-757899113d89.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Corroborates that the note was publicly reported before May 8, 2026; identifies Judge Karas release, NYT petition, Tartaglione discovery claim, note language supporting final-message intent, and adverse uncertainty about authorship and government-report omissions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T04:30:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"757899113d8967676e74909d141f7d97d4735bd8d75a4af34fb3950b18d871e1\",\"size_bytes\":2552,\"source_description\":\"PBS NewsHour page carrying Associated Press reporting by Michael R. Sisak and Larry Neumeister, published May 6, 2026 and updated May 7, 2026; retrieved/rendered during this AAR run.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.pbs.org/newshour/nation/judge-releases-note-that-cellmate-says-he-found-after-epsteins-suspected-suicide-attempt\",\"storage_name\":\"75/757899113d8967676e74909d141f7d97d4735bd8d75a4af34fb3950b18d871e1\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"PBS/AP May 6-7, 2026 report on Epstein note release - relevant extracted text\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T04:24:14Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_90fa205907f7_market-page\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"market-page.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"90fa205907f7af6483463b7dcda6e06a38a2e22fbe19312319fdf46a78f14646\",\"size_bytes\":4641,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"90/90fa205907f7af6483463b7dcda6e06a38a2e22fbe19312319fdf46a78f14646\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"system\",\"submitted_phase\":\"case_packet\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"market-page.txt\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T04:24:14Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_b3b39b867ad2_official-source-record\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"official-source-record.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"b3b39b867ad2e11f9a30b457a4346cfaf68a0fbde9b52a73b02948e8bf4a44f6\",\"size_bytes\":1944,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"b3/b3b39b867ad2e11f9a30b457a4346cfaf68a0fbde9b52a73b02948e8bf4a44f6\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"system\",\"subm